   <text>
      <body>
         <div type="translation">
            <ab>Year 7 of the Emperor Caesar Marcus Antonius Gordianus Pius Felix Augustus, in Choiak, for the arithmesis of Hathyr. Euporous, weaver, has paid to the account of the nomarchia, through me, Aurelius Didymos, four drachmai, equal 4 dr.</ab>
